ympics|Olympic Games]]\n|rowspan=2|[[London]], United Kingdom\n|bgcolor=gold|1st\n|[[Athletics at the 2012 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's 5000 metres|5000 m]]\n|13:41.66\n|-\n|bgcolor=gold|1st\n|[[Athletics at the 2012 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's 10,000 metres|10,000 m]]\n|27:30.42\n|-\n|rowspan=3|2013\n|[[2013 European Team Championships|European Team Championships]]\n|[[Gateshead]], United Kingdom\n|bgcolor=gold|1st\n|5000 m\n|14:10.00\n|-\n|rowspan=2|[[2013 World Championships in Athletics|World Championships]]\n|rowspan=2|[[Moscow]], Russia\n|bgcolor=gold|1st\n|[[2013 World Championships in Athletics \u2013 Men's 5000 metres|5000 m]]\n|13:26.98\n|-\n|bgcolor=gold|1st\n|[[2013 World Championships in Athletics \u2013 Men's 10,000 metres|10,000 m]]\n|27:21.71\n|-\n|rowspan=2|2014\n|rowspan=2|[[2014 European Athletics Championships|European Championships]]\n|rowspan=2|[[Z\u00fcrich]], Switzerland\n|bgcolor=gold|1st\n|[[2014 European Athletics Championships \u2013 Men's 5000 metres|5000 m]]\n|14:05.82\n|-\n|bgcolor=gold|1st\n|[[2014 European Athletics Championships \u2013 Men's 10,000 metres|10,000 m]]\n|28:08.11\n|-\n|rowspan=2|2015\n|rowspan=2|[[2015 World Championships in Athletics|World Championships]]\n|rowspan=2|[[Beijing]], China\n|bgcolor=gold|1st\n|[[2015 World Championships in Athletics \u2013 Men's 5000 metres|5000 m]]\n|13:50.38\n|-\n|bgcolor=gold|1st\n|[[2015 World Championships in Athletics \u2013 Men's 10,000 metres|10,000 m]]\n|27:01.13\n|-\n|rowspan=3|2016\n|[[2016 IAAF World Half Marathon Championships|World Half Marathon Championships]]\n|[[Cardiff]], United Kingdom\n|style=\"background:#c96;\"|3rd\n|Individual\n|59:59\n|-\n|rowspan=2|[[Athletics at the 2016 Summer Olympics|Olympic Games]]\n|rowspan=2|[[Rio de Janeiro]], Brazil\n|bgcolor=gold|1st\n|[[Athletics at the 2016 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's 5,000 metres|5000 m]]\n|13:03.30\n|-\n|bgcolor=gold|1st\n|[[Athletics at the 2016 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's 10,000 metres|10,000 m]]\n|27:05.17\n|-\