nts|1526006}}\n| {{nts|369.59}}\n| {{nts|6096120}}\n| \n| {{nts|}}\n|{{nts|}}\n|-\n| align=left | [[Atlanta]]\n| align=left | {{flagg|pspew|al=c|pref=List of cities in the|USA}}\n| align=center | [[File:Midtown HDR Atlanta.jpg|125px]]\n| {{nts|5572000}}\n| align=left | \n| {{nts|420003}}\n| {{nts|354.22}}\n| {{nts|5949951}}\n| {{nts|21690}}\n|{{nts|}}\n|{{nts|}}\n|-\n| align=left | [[Fukuoka]]\n| align=left | {{flagg|pspew|al=c|pref=List of cities in|Japan}}\n| align=center | [[File:20100718 Fukuoka 2870.jpg|125px]]\n| {{nts|5551000}}\n| align=left | [[Cities designated by government ordinance of Japan|Designated city]]\n| {{nts|1588924}}\n| {{nts|343.39}}\n| {{nts|2565501}}\n| \n|{{nts|}}\n|{{nts|}}\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Khartoum]]\n| align=\"left\" |{{flagg|pspew|al=c|pref=List of cities in|Sudan}}\n| align=\"center\" |[[File:\u0627\u0644\u062e\u0631\u0637\u0648\u0645-\u062c\u0632\u064a\u0631\u0629 \u062a\u0648\u062a\u064a.jpg|125px]]\n|{{nts|5534000}}\n| align=\"left\" |\n|{{nts|639,598}}\n|{{nts|22142}}\n|{{nts|5274321}}\n| \n|{{nts|}}\n|{{nts|}}\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Barcelona]]\n| align=\"left\" |{{flagg|pspew|al=c|pref=List of cities in|Spain}}\n| align=\"center\" |[[File:Central business district of Barcelona (2).JPG|125px]]\n|{{nts|5494000}}\n| align=\"left\" |[[Municipalities of Catalonia|Municipality]]\n|{{nts|1620343}}<ref>Municipal Register of Spain 2018. National Statistics Institute.</ref>\n|{{nts|101.4}}\n|{{nts|5474482}}<ref name=\"eurostat\">[http://appsso.eurostat.ec.europa.eu/nui/show.do?dataset=met_pjanaggr3&lang=en Population on 1 January by broad age group, sex and metropolitan regions] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160822103143/http://appsso.eurostat.ec.europa.eu/nui/show.do?dataset=met_pjanaggr3&lang=en |date=22 August 2016 }} - [[Eurostat]], 2017</ref>\n| \n|\n|\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Johannesburg]]\n| align=\"left\" |{{flagg|pspew|al=c|pref=List of cities in|South Africa}}\n| align=\"center\" |[[File:The Wits University East Campus (archived).jpg|125px]]\n|{{nts|5486000}}\n| align=\"left\" |[[Metropolitan municipality (South Africa)|Metropolitan municipality]]\n|{{nts|}}\n|{{nts|}}\n|{{nts|}}\n| \n|{{nts|}}\n|{{nts|}}\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Saint Petersburg]]\n| align=\"left\" |{{flagg|pspew|al=c|pref=List of cities in|Russia}}\n| align=\"center\" |[[File:Spb Vasilievsky Island Neva at SchmidtEmb asv2019-09.jpg|125px]]\n|{{nts|5383000}}\n| align=\"left\" |[[Federal cities of Russia|Federal city]]\n|{{nts|}}\n|{{nts|}}\n|{{nts|}}\n| \n|{{nts|}}\n|{{nts|}}\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Qingdao]]\n| align=\"left\" |{{flagg|pspew|al=c|pref=List of cities in|China}}\n| align=\"center\" |[[File:Qingdao picture.jpg|125px]]\n|{{nts|5381000}}\n| align=\"left\" |[[Prefecture-level city|City]] ([[Sub-provincial divisions in the People's Republic of China|sub-provincial]])\n|{{nts|}}\n|{{nts|}}\n|{{nts|}}\n| \n|{{nts|}}\n|{{nts|}}\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Dalian]]\n| align=\"left\" |{{flagg|pspew|al=c|pref=List of cities in|China}}\n| align=\"center\" |[[File:DalianSkyline.JPG|125px]]\n|{{nts|5300000}}\n| align=\"left\" |[[Prefecture-level city|City]] ([[Sub-provincial divisions in the People's Republic of China|sub-provincial]])\n|{{nts|}}\n|{{nts|}}\n|{{nts|}}\n| \n|{{nts|}}\n|{{nts|}}\n|-\n| align=left | [[Washington, D.C.]]\n| align=left | {{flagg|pspew|al=c|pref=List of cities in the|USA}}\n| align=center | [[File:Washington, D.C. - 2007 aerial view.jpg|125px]]\n| {{nts|5207000}}\n| align=left | [[Federal district]]\n| {{nts|702,455}}<ref name=\"USA\"/>\n| {{nts|177}}\n| {{nts|6,263,245}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.citypopulation.de/en/usa/metro/47900__washington_arlington_/|title=Washington - Arlington - Alexandria (Metropolitan Statistical Area, Metropolitan Areas, USA) - Population Statistics, Charts, Map and Location|website=www.citypopulation.de}}</ref>\n| {{nts|17,009}}\n| {{nts|7,515,000}}\n| {{nts|5,281}}{{efn|Includes the city of [[Baltimore]].}}\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Yangon]]\n| align=\"left\" |{{flagg|pspew|al=c|pref=List of cities in|Myanmar}}\n| align=\"center\" |[[File:Yangon downtown at night.jpg|125px]]\n|{{nts|5157000}}\n| align=\"left\" |[[List of cities and largest towns in Myanmar|City]]\n|{{nts|}}\n|{{nts|}}\n|{{nts|}}\n| \n|{{nts|}}\n|{{nts|}}\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Alexandria]]\n| align=\"left\" |{{flagg|pspew|al=c|pref=List of cities in|Egypt}}\n| align=\"center\" |[[File:Alexandria - Egypt.jpg|125px]]\n|{{nts|5086000}}\n| align=\"left\" |[[Governorates of Egypt|Urban governorate]]\n|{{nts|}}\n|{{nts|}}\n|{{nts|}}\n| \n|{{nts|}}\n|{{nts|}}\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Jinan]]\n| align=\"left\" |{{flagg|pspew|al=c|pref=List of cities in|China}}\n| align=\"center\" |[[File:Jinanfromqianfoshan.jpg|125px]]\n|{{nts|5052000}}\n| align=\"left\" |[[Prefecture-level city|City]] ([[Sub-provincial divisions in the People's Republic of China|sub-provincial]])\n|{{nts|8700000}}\n|{{nts|10244}}\n|{{nts|11000000}}\n|{{nts|53000}}\n|{{nts|}}\n|{{nts|}}\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Guadalajara]]\n| align=\"left\" |{{flagg|pspew|al=c|pref=List of cities in|Mexico}}\n| align=\"center\" |[[File:Guadalajara 16 feb 2013 (cropped).jpg|125px]]\n|{{nts|5023000}}\n| align=\"left\" |[[Municipalities of Mexico|Municipality]]\n|{{nts|1460148}}\n|{{nts|151}}\n|{{nts|5002466}}\n|{{nts|2734}}\n|{{nts|}}\n|{{nts|}}\n|-\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [[List of largest cities throughout history]]\n* [[List of towns and cities with 100,000 or more inhabitants]]\n* [[Number of urban areas by country]]\n\n==Notes==\n{{notelist}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://data.un.org/Data.aspx?d=POP&f=tableCode%3A240 UNSD Demographics Statistics \u2013 City population by sex, city and city type] \n* [https://nordpil.com/resources/world-database-of-large-cities/ Nordpil World Database of Large Urban Areas, 1950\u20132050]\n\n{{World's largest cities}}\n{{Cities}}\n{{portal bar|Geography|Lists}}\n\n[[Category:Cities-related lists of superlatives]]\n